{"tid":984517,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"先鋒基金創始人Jack Bogle過世","createTime":"2019-01-17T00:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T01:25:02.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5c0050dd6cb0b0b001ebc60495a9b5e487f790","tid":984517,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:58:30.000Z","msg":"17日早間消息，據美國媒體報導，先鋒集團創始人、&ldquo;指數基金之父&rdquo;傑克-伯格（Jack Bogle）去世，享年89歲。<br />\n <br />\n　　伯格是全球首隻指數共同基金的創始人，他的先鋒集團目前管理資產超過5.1萬億美元。他被認為是全球最偉大的投資者之一。他的指數共同基金使投資者能夠獲得高回報，而成本低於積極管理基金。<br />\n <br />\n　　1975年，他創立了全球最大的共同基金先鋒集團，後來擔任董事長兼CEO，直到1996年。先鋒現在為大約170個國家的2000多萬投資者管理資產。<br />\n <br />\n　　但伯格的個人財富相對較少，據估計8000萬美元，他有心臟病史，31歲時患了心臟病，總共發作過六次，65歲時接受了心臟移植手術。<br />\n <br />\n　　他寫了13本關於投資的書，最近的一本是2018年的《堅持下去：先鋒和指數革命的故事》（Stay the Course： The Story of Vanguard and the Index Revolution）"},{"pid":"8ab3fe2ed39339293fa40a501fbf3d5e2c1ee75b","tid":984517,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:59:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"234a70d48bd6bc38941e71e8693543882e68efaf","tid":984517,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"Twitter 剛剛睇到"},{"pid":"d8d036cca792c3477291631f73d72039ab20fca0","tid":984517,"uid":158480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"R.i.p.<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67b0c74abd3216973cf19e02aec037ce37806cd","tid":984517,"uid":56732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:40:42.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79045eacf5773cf8ca92cc26f3ce712bd152df70","tid":984517,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:08:26.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a08284f678f4328efc796b52806a7f6e3b783f9","tid":984517,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":2